      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. the \"weary resignation\" thing is definitely a vibe. to push the horror aspect further, i want to lean into why people are actually afraid of the area. can you add some details about the \"undercurrent\" of what's happening there? like, what are the rumors or the specific things people say about the people living there or the things that happen in those alleys at night that make it feel so unpredictable or threatening?",
